{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-08-24-how-to-add-red-asterisk-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aHoisting! To add red asterisk in react js, you can apply  on asterisk. It will add red asterisk in react js. Today, I am going to‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To add red asterisk in react js, you can apply <code class=\"language-text\">style={{ color: 'red' }}</code> on asterisk. It will add red asterisk in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add red asterisk in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import react component.</h3>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Create a Component.</h3>\n<p>You can use <code class=\"language-text\">style={{ color: 'red' }}</code> to add red asterisk in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>label<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>span style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">color</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'red'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>span<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Add red asterisk example.</h3>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">react</code> and set <code class=\"language-text\">style={{ color: 'red' }}</code> on asterisk to add red asterisk in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> label <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>label<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>span style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">color</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'red'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>span<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">style={{ color: 'red' }}</code> to add red asterisk in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 291px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/52656d22043b651996d6285bba0e14cc/73915/red-asterisk.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.37974683544303%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRooAAABXRUJQVlA4WAoAAAAQAAAAEwAADwAAQUxQSBQAAAABF/D3/4iIQiCQ7A8S7QAR/c9OAFZQOCBQAAAAcAMAnQEqFAAQAD7RVqRLqCSjobAIAQAaCUAAC30XNiAmPVkAAPqf5VKvLyxTM+TEaIPIOEiJX7N7HT/4mvQFYxrKLkK7uDM9G8hldiHgAAA='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, add, red, asterisk\"\n        title=\"React, add, red, asterisk\"\n        src=\"/static/52656d22043b651996d6285bba0e14cc/73915/red-asterisk.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/52656d22043b651996d6285bba0e14cc/81b7c/red-asterisk.webp 158w,\n/static/52656d22043b651996d6285bba0e14cc/73915/red-asterisk.webp 291w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 291px) 100vw, 291px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to add red asterisk in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"August 24, 2024","description":"Example of add red asterisk in react js with step by step tutorial - aHoisting","social_image":{"absolutePath":"/Users/mac/Documents/hoisting/ahoisting/static/media/template/reactjs.jpg"}}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add rainbow color in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-08-24-how-to-add-rainbow-color-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add qr code in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-08-23-how-to-add-qr-code-in-react/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2024-08-24-how-to-add-red-asterisk-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2024-08-24-how-to-add-rainbow-color-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2024-08-23-how-to-add-qr-code-in-react/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2555585279","2714594843","3159585216"]}